
The objective of Enron Government Affairs is to provide quality service to 
the business units it supports while controlling overall costs.  Regulatory 
Risk & Analytics is available to provide information and assistance to Enron 
Government Affairs staff when managing regulatory risk/opportunity, and 
developing a framework for valuation of regulatory and political activities.  
Regulatory Risk & Analytics is charged with measuring how Public Affairs' 
advocacy is advancing Enron's vision.

John Neslage should be contacted for these and other related matters at 
713-853-6827.


